{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idaac69d91-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6212"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6212"},"text":"§ 6212.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Multi-year plan for clean-up","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of Energy shall develop and implement a multi-year plan for the clean-up of nuclear waste at the Savannah River Site that results, or has resulted, from the following:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaac69d92-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6212/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Nuclear weapons activities carried out at the site.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaac69d93-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6212/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The processing, treating, packaging, and disposal of Department of Energy domestic and foreign spent nuclear fuel rods at the site.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idaac69d94-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/119/60/dC/tXXXI/s3111/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 119–60, div. C, title XXXI, § 3111(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2025-12-18"},"text":"Dec. 18, 2025","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/139/1401"},"text":"139 Stat. 1401","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idaac69d95-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idaac69d96-3a6f-11f1-a5